0.name: 1Wet note
0.text:
I woke up to screams of terror.
The city is sinking!

All is flooded we need to leave.
Only the bridge can save us!

... The bridge is gone. No hope.
I need to find a higher point.
Goodbye

1.name: 2Wet note
1.text:
I woke up to screams of terror.
The city is sinking!

All is flooded we need to leave.
Will the bridge be gone?

It's gone! I need to find a higher point.
Goodbye

2.name: 3Wet note
2.text:
I woke up to screams of terror. But less than in my dreams.
The city is sinking! Again!

Something is wrong.. This is.. unnatrual.
All who died are gone this time.
I saw a platform rise around 5pm.
I need to find a higher point.
 That way I will survive.

3.name: 4Wet note
3.text:
It's all real! Every time!.
The city sinks but at midnight, the city returns.
But all who die stay dead.

I am the only one left!
The hallway is flooding again.

I might not make it this time.
Time is repeating...
